OL,3,CCancer fundraiser 'emotional' after
OL,4,Cstanding ovation at Six Nations match
OL,6,F"I wouldn't have completed the
OL,7,Fchallenge without all the support I've
OL,8,Fhad," Craig said.
OL,10,F"From my fellow walkers and
OL,11,Fcelebrities to the people who have
OL,12,Fcome out to support us in towns and
OL,13,Fvillages across Wales, the support has
OL,14,Fbeen overwhelming."
OL,16,FCraig had carried the ball for the
OL,17,FWales v France match throughout the
OL,18,Fchallenge and brought it onto the
OL,19,Fpitch for Sunday's game.
