OL,3,CCancer fundraiser 'emotional' after
OL,4,Cstanding ovation at Six Nations match
OL,6,FMet with a standing ovation from the
OL,7,Fcrowd of over 71,000 fans, he was
OL,8,Fjoined on the pitch by his wife
OL,9,FTracey, daughter Isla, and son Zach.
OL,11,FThe former WRU boss is aiming to raise
OL,12,F#1 million for the Maxwell Family Fund
OL,13,Fto improve and develop the cancer
OL,14,Fpathway in Wales.
OL,16,FAbout 600 walkers had signed up to
OL,17,Fsupport Craig on the 26-day challenge,
OL,18,Fwhich covered 780 miles of the coast
OL,19,Fpath to represent the 78 days it took
OL,20,FCraig to receive his diagnosis from
OL,21,Fthe point of finding his tumour.
