OL,3,CCancer fundraiser 'emotional' after
OL,4,Cstanding ovation at Six Nations match
OL,6,FDuring the challenge, he was joined by
OL,7,Fa number of familiar celebrity faces,
OL,8,Fincluding TV presenter Gethin Jones,
OL,9,Fcomedian Rhod Gilbert, weatherman
OL,10,FDerek Brockway and former rugby
OL,11,Fplayers Sam Warburton, Jamie Roberts
OL,12,Fand Josh Navidi.
OL,14,FFormer England cricket captain Sir
OL,15,FAndrew Strauss also joined for a leg,
OL,16,Fhaving lost his wife Ruth to lung
OL,17,Fcancer in 2018.
