OL,6,FOn Sunday, 11 March, he walked from
OL,7,FBarry to Cardiff, stopping at Penarth,
OL,8,Fwhere he received a warm welcome from
OL,9,Fhis hometown, including Penarth RFC's
OL,10,Fjunior rugby team, who he coaches.
OL,12,FAs he walked in the , rugby pundit
OL,13,FJonathan Davies, said: "I have been
OL,14,Fwith him on many challenges but he is
OL,15,Ffacing the toughest challenge of his
OL,16,Flife now.
