OL,3,CCancer fundraiser 'emotional' after
OL,4,Cstanding ovation at Six Nations match
OL,6,F"What he has done is absolutely
OL,7,Fphenomenal. You can see how the rugby
OL,8,Ffamily comes together. The support he
OL,9,Fhas had. He has done this to show his
OL,10,Fchildren that even in the darkest
OL,11,Ftimes you can be a force for good.
OL,12,FThis guy is an absolute inspiration."
OL,14,FThanking everyone who has supported
OL,15,Fhim Mr Maxwell added: "These people
OL,16,Fhave lifted me every day and kept me
OL,17,Fgoing.
