OL,3,CCancer fundraiser 'emotional' after
OL,4,Cstanding ovation at Six Nations match
OL,6,F"Walking the match ball onto the pitch
OL,7,Fwith my family, surrounded by former
OL,8,FWRU and Six Nations colleagues and
OL,9,Fover 70,000 fans, was emotional and
OL,10,Fsomething that will stay with me any
OL,11,Fmy family forever.
OL,13,F"Thank you to everyone who has
OL,14,Fsupported the challenge. We're hoping
OL,15,Fthat everyone will keep donating so
OL,16,Fthat we can reach our #1m target."
